OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAny early showery outbreaks
OL,6,Ffading, then generally dry with some
OL,7,Fhazy sunshine developing through the
OL,8,Fmorning. Cloud increasing into the
OL,9,Fevening with a risk of some showery
OL,10,Frain, perhaps giving the odd heavier
OL,11,Fburst. Light or gentle winds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FAny showery outbreaks of rain
OL,14,Fat first, will gradually weaken
OL,15,Fovernight to leave a rather cloudy,
OL,16,Fbut mainly dry start to Tuesday. Fog
OL,17,Fpatches across the Peak District.
OL,18,FLight winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
