OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FGenerally dry with variable
OL,6,Fcloud but warm, bright spells
OL,7,Fdeveloping. However, thicker cloud and
OL,8,Frain arriving from the west through
OL,9,Fthe evening. Turning breezier later.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,12,FCloudier on Wednesday with some rain
OL,13,Flikely. Thursday and Friday, mostly
OL,14,Fdry with bright or sunny spells.
OL,15,FTurning very warm, and perhaps more
OL,16,Fhumid. Winds generally light.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
